label: AB9_hP20_194_c_bfk-001
title: CeH$_{9}$ Structure
comments:
(Li, 2019) found CeH$_{9}$ stable above 100 GPa in space group $P6_{3}/mmc$ \#194.  The atomic structure shown here is taken from their first-principles calculations. 
 The ICSD entry is from the slightly later work of (Salke, 2019).
